content:
Grant Permission to the Analytics Integration User

Assign the integration user with the Vlocity CMT license to allow them access to all the fields in the app.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Developer edition and for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.
From Setup, enter Installed Packages in the Quick Find box, and then click Installed Packages.
Look for the Vlocity CMT package, and click Manage Licenses.
Click Add Users.
Select the Integration User.
Click Add.
Save your changes.

Data Requirements to Create the Analytics for Communications - Consumer App
Set Field-Level Security to Enable Creation of the Analytics for Communications - Consumer App
title: Granting Permission for Analytics Integration User
